means: 不能抵抗的，无抵抗力的

sentence.Network_en: The grain seemed impelled with a force of its own, a resistless, huge force.
sentence.Network_cn: 这些粮食好象是给自己的力量, 给一股势不可当, 巨大无比的力量驱使着.

sentence.Network_en: Be his Banner unconquered , resistless his spear.
sentence.Network_cn: 祝他旗开得胜, 所向无敌.

sentence.Network_en: Sincerity has such resistless charms ; she oft the fiercest of our foes disarms.
sentence.Network_cn: 真诚的魔力如此不可抵抗, 最凶猛的敌人也常被它解除武装.
